summary:
In recent years I have developed myself into a chemist with a feeling for quality. I would like to continue my career in an energizing job in the direction of Research and Development within the chemical or related industries. I am structured and neat with a creative analytical view and have an interest in procedures and systems.

Specialties: working with virtual teams, compiling of test methods and standards, data analysis and excel
